      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW BRODY (2) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 1.5 lengths into second (22.13) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature in the finish again. RAM RAID (4) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (22.28) at this track over 390m. Yet to taste defeat from three runs out of this box. Bold showing expected. JARMON (8) recorded a win over the 390m at this track in a quick 22.24 last start. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. PAW PASCAL (1) is likely to have admirers.",
